          <p><strong>A dead collar means your dog has zero protection. None.</strong> Your boundary vanishes. Your dog doesn&rsquo;t know that &mdash; but the road doesn&rsquo;t care. Battery life was one of my biggest fears, and SpotOn Nova put that fear to rest.</p>
