            </div>
          </div>
          <p>In my real-world testing, I consistently got 32-34 hours per charge with tracking enabled. That means your dog never loses protection while you sleep. The magnetic USB-C charging is a game-changer &mdash; it snaps on easily, even with muddy hands, and a full charge takes about an hour.</p>
          <p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> I developed a simple routine of plugging the collar in during dinner every other day. This completely eliminated any battery anxiety and my dog was never without protection. Not for a single minute.</p>
